ActForeign Missions and International Organizations Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Commission for Environmental Cooperation Privileges and Immunities in Canada Order
PrecisOrder amending the COMMISSION FOR ENVIRONMENTAL COOPERATION PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES IN CANADA ORDER in order to (1) remove references to the North American Agreement on Environmental Cooperation and to refer instead to the Environmental Cooperation Agreement; and (2) remove references to the 1997 Headquarters Agreement and to refer instead to the 2020 Headquarters Agreement.
